You probably mean the Sharp GP1U5x. That one is modifiable so that it can
be read like an analog signal.

If anyone can direct me to a company in the Netherlands which sells these
parts, I would very much like to know. Thanks.

>Be carefull by the way, the pin lay-out is different:
>
>Sharp IS1U60
>1: out
>2: gnd
>3: vcc
>
>Siemens SFH506-36
>1: gnd
>2: vcc
>3: out
>
